{"type":null,"faqId":35078,"title":"My phone's Wi-Fi connection automatically disconnects after the screen times out. What can I do?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>Change the Wi-Fi sleep policy as follows: </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Touch S</span><span class=\"s1\">ettings</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">WLAN</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">advanced menu</span><span>&gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Keep Wi-Fi on during sleep</span><span>, and select </span><span class=\"s1\">Always</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Note: By default, </span><span class=\"s1\">Always</span><span> is selected for </span><span class=\"s1\">Keep Wi-Fi on during sleep</span><span>. If the settings are modified, your phone disconnects from the Wi-Fi network when its screen turns off. The following describes the three options of </span><span class=\"s1\">Keep Wi-Fi on during sleep</span><span>:</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">Always</span><span>: Never disconnect a Wi-Fi connection.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">Only when plugged in</span><span>: The Wi-Fi connection never disconnects when your phone is charging. If your phone is not charging, it disconnects a Wi-Fi connection when it has been idle for 3 minutes.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"_Toc342402049\"><span class=\"s1\">Never (increase data usage)</span><span>: The Wi-Fi connection disconnects when your phone has been idle for </span><span>16 </span><span>minutes.</span></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=111412\" style=\"width:1.8048611in;height:3.2020833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=111413\" style=\"width:1.7069445in;height:3.0409722in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=111414\" style=\"width:1.6888889in;height:3.007639in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"9819","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1437034667000,"seriesProductName":"Y541-U02","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"HONOR BEE DUAL SIM ( Y541-U02 )","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}